{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b295f1c369","title":"在修改《欢呼北大的一张大字报》一文时加的一段","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9ff8e3148d","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":5,"articleId":"b295f1c369"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2b47ddf8a8","type":"paragraph","text":"生的文化大革命行动看来，我不相信有正民主，正克思主义，而是站在资产阶级方面反对无产阶级文化大革命。团中央不仅不支持青年学生运动，反而压学生运动，我看该处理。","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b295f1c369"},{"id":"7be439f85c","type":"paragraph","text":"炮打司合部","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b295f1c369"},{"id":"807d7a522f","type":"paragraph","text":"我的一张大字报","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b295f1c369"},{"id":"001e8f5f1d","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年八月五日）","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b295f1c369"},{"id":"9e0376b2be","type":"paragraph","text":"全国第一张马列主义的大字报和《人民日报》评论员的评论，写得何等好呵！腊同志们重读一通这张大字报和这个评论。可是在五十多天里，从中央到地方的某些领导同志，却反其道而行之，站在反动的资产阶级立场上，实行资产阶级专政，将无产阶级轰轰烈烈的文化大革命运动打下去，倒是非，混潘黑白，围剩革命派，压制不同意见，实行白色恐饰，自以为得意，长资产阶级的威风，灭无产阶级的志气，又何其毒也！联系到一九六二年的右倾和一九六四年的形“左”而实右的错澳倾向，自不是可以发人深醒的吗？","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b295f1c369"},{"id":"916567c671","type":"paragraph","text":"毛东在修改《欢呼北大的一张大字报》","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b295f1c369"},{"id":"a3c7dd2abf","type":"paragraph","text":"一文时加的一段器","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b295f1c369"},{"id":"e523d6b1a8","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年八月五日）","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b295f1c369"},{"id":"74c1ebcb79","type":"paragraph","text":"危害革命的错识领导，不应当无条件接受，而应当坚决抵制。在这次文化大革命中，广大革命师生及革命干部对于错误的领导，就广泛地进行过抵制","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b295f1c369"},{"id":"51ed6cf6fd","type":"paragraph","text":"在中共中央基众接待站的斋","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b295f1c369"},{"id":"1549b3bc58","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年八月十日）你们要关心国家大事，要把无产阶级文化大革命进行到底！","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b295f1c369"},{"id":"2ce22801e6","type":"paragraph","text":"对檬黄田大字报的批示","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b295f1c369"},{"id":"51eaeed8f0","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年八月）印发全会（指十一中全会）各同志。将杨寅田大字报题目用特号字，全文用老五号刊出。","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b295f1c369"},{"id":"a59e8b694c","type":"paragraph","text":"·267","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b295f1c369"}],"page":{"id":"417f5f0fd1","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"b295f1c369","start":280,"end":280}}}},"__N_SSG":true}